.TH "libnvme_export_tls_key_versioned" 9 "libnvme_export_tls_key_versioned" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_export_tls_key_versioned \- Export a TLS pre-shared key
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" libnvme_export_tls_key_versioned
.BI "(struct libnvme_global_ctx *ctx "  ","
.BI "unsigned char version "  ","
.BI "unsigned char hmac "  ","
.BI "const unsigned char *key_data "  ","
.BI "size_t key_len "  ","
.BI "char **identity "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
struct libnvme_global_ctx object
.IP "version" 12
Indicated the representation of the TLS PSK
.IP "hmac" 12
HMAC algorithm used to transfor the configured PSK
in a retained PSK
.IP "key_data" 12
Raw data of the key
.IP "key_len" 12
Length of \fIkey_data\fP
.IP "identity" 12
TLS identity to return
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns \fIkey_data\fP in the PSK Interchange format as defined in section
3.6.1.5 of the NVMe TCP Transport specification.

It is the responsibility of the caller to free the returned
string.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or negative error code otherwise
